@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_whrecb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.75 + tmp + 0.73)) - v2)
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.63 + v2 + 0.99) + (tmp + 0.35 * v1 + 0.00)) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.37 * tmp + 0.38)))
    data[tid] = v0
